    "title": "マイペース・タキオン",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "トレーナー君、明日は9時に駅前集合だ。\r\n忘れずにきたまえよ。",
            "enText": "Trainer, we will meet in front\nof the station at 9:00 tomorrow.\nDon't forget to come.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "いきなり何の話？",
                    "enText": "What are you talking about\nall of a sudden?",
                    "nextBlock": 2
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": -7805330980500107849
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 3013275943978431557
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6767433162324781345,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "聞いていなかったのかい？\r\n……いや、言っていなかったか。まぁいい。",
            "enText": "You weren't listening, were you?…\nNo, you didn't tell me. That's okay.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": -8735945793374674467
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": -4754800384854769172
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6043440916432413157,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "知り合いの伝手でね、実験に使用する\r\n器具や薬品なんかが安く手に入るんだ。",
            "enText": "Through a friend of mine, I was able to\nget some equipment and chemicals for my\nexperiments at a reasonable price.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -4131286784204363714
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": 4419558585811771069
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8584347080008663628,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "今やっている実験がちょうど佳境で、\r\nすぐにでも器具が必要なんだよ。",
            "enText": "The experiment I'm working on right now is\njust reaching its climax, and I need the\nequipment right away.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 53,
                    "pathId": -2383028178775970302
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": 1031715722401313177
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2862529626728860525,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "いいかい、君は荷物持ちだ。\r\n9時に駅前、忘れずに来るように。",
            "enText": "Remember, you're a baggage handler. Don't\nforget to come to the station at 9:00.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 55,
                    "pathId": -1963815122210818498
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": -8105948702554519602
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3891939971241931540,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "翌朝、9時に駅前で待っていたのだが――\r\n10時をまわっても、11時をまわっても、\nアグネスタキオンは現れない。",
            "enText": "The next morning, I waited in front\nof the station at nine o'clock, but\nAgnes Tachyon didn't show up until\nten or eleven o'clock.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 118,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 52,
                    "pathId": -3781658775021697201
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 52,
                    "pathId": 4553219354921450146
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1110455358932067858,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "もしや、何かあったのでは……と\r\n思っていると、アグネスタキオンから\nスマホに着信があった。",
            "enText": "As I was wondering if there was something\nwrong with…, I received a call on my\nphone from Agnes Tachyon.",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "pathId": 7588775840711284551,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "『くっ……トレーナー君……』",
            "enText": "\"Stick to…, trainer,…\"",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "タキオン！？",
                    "enText": "Tachyons!",
                    "nextBlock": 9
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6715698639606178810,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "『校舎……裏、に……\r\nはや、く……来るんだ……！』",
            "enText": "\"Come… to the back…\nof the school building… as\nsoon as possible…!\"",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "pathId": -2633277120486919999,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "(バタッ)",
            "enText": "(Slap)",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 51,
            "pathId": 4067758073206621533,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "一体、何が……！？\r\n校舎裏にいるのだろうか。\n急いで向かうことにした。",
            "enText": "What the hell is…! Is it in the back\nof the school building? I decided to hurry\nand head there.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 72,
                    "pathId": 5122836531128104780
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 54,
                    "pathId": 677083488908191906
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -2821911171879191793
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -9047987573722402858,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "やぁ……トレーナー君……。",
            "enText": "Hello,… trainer,…",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 114,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "大丈夫か！？",
                    "enText": "Are you okay?",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "大丈夫！？",
                    "enText": "Great man!",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 182,
                    "pathId": 4867467622268459290
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 135,
                    "pathId": 5517703114120908651
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 139,
                    "pathId": 6162257873757166968
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8888261058354460850,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "ここで実験をしていたんだ……\r\nそうしたら……意識が遠のいてね……。",
            "enText": "I was experimenting here… and then I\n… went into a daze…",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 3186003816622584001
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 32,
                    "pathId": 3773292245513154694
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": 8088052348043179296
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8054961424896725340,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "実験に夢中で、しばらく食事を\r\nとるのを忘れていたみたいだ……。",
            "enText": "She was so engrossed in the experiment that\nshe forgot to eat for a while…",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 86,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 39,
                    "pathId": -172552952963018454
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 97,
                    "pathId": 1119458418750392200
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3309890749562596397,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "タンパク質、ビタミン、糖分、\r\nあらゆる栄養素が……。",
            "enText": "Proteins, vitamins, sugars, and all kinds\nof nutrients are available at…",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 41,
                    "pathId": 4136628546775621504
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": 4082007315081358497
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7853029209957847912,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "……ああ、また意識が遠くに……。\r\nトレーナー君、何か……栄養を……くれ……。",
            "enText": "… Oh, my consciousness is far…\naway again. Trainer, give me some…\nnutrition…",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "我慢して待ってて！",
                    "enText": "Just be patient and wait!",
                    "nextBlock": 17
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "すぐに用意する！",
                    "enText": "We'll have it ready soon!",
                    "nextBlock": 25
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 68,
                    "pathId": 3177115794388563996
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -5141761503092182549
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8142400492215276068,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "うう……はやくー……。",
            "enText": "Ugh… hurry up…",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 66,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 54,
                    "pathId": -6066677298985004942
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 77,
                    "pathId": -1316024750450986108
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4295839125198303122,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "カフェテリアで目に入ったものを\r\n手あたり次第に皿にのせ、\nアグネスタキオンへと届けた。",
            "enText": "I put whatever I saw in the cafeteria\non my plate and delivered it\nto Agnes Tachyon.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 102,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 52,
                    "pathId": -7786500939685231429
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 52,
                    "pathId": -385384665094257199
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1377444749919545144,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "ふぅー……食べたなぁ。\r\nいやはや、危ないところだった。",
            "enText": "Whew… You ate that. Oh\nno, that was a close one.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 138,
                    "pathId": 5727465155822286274
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 154,
                    "pathId": 1906743469734595012
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8872779282225793122,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "頑張って待っていたかいがあったよ。\r\nご苦労だったね、トレーナー君。",
            "enText": "It was worth the wait. Thank you\nfor your hard work, trainer.",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": 515234292684683319
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": -7114446191390357823
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4080360971816451083,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "それにしても……ハハッ、山盛りだったな！\r\nどれだけ心配性なんだ、君は！",
            "enText": "But still,… haha, that was a pile of\ncrap! How worried you must be, you!",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 54,
                    "pathId": -981284906998565830
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -9120595801694231507
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6316234041308941226,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "はー……とにかくまぁ、助かった。",
            "enText": "Ha… Anyway, well,\nthank you for the help.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 65,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": 7025854199116489763
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": 6958530671796973240
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3723217383226971556,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "今後は食事を忘れないよう、\r\n気をつけることにするよ。",
            "enText": "I'll be careful not to forget\nto eat in the future.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 80,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 46,
                    "pathId": -9171004616724294927
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 91,
                    "pathId": 958551442849017271
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3054279637661554163,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "お腹を撫でながら、\r\nアグネスタキオンは何かを学んだように\n満足そうな顔をしていた。",
            "enText": "As I stroked her belly, Agnes Tachyon\nlooked satisfied, as if she had\nlearned something.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": -302492572488399677
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": 539673481853337468
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6786349806546485130,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "急いでくれたまえ……。",
            "enText": "Hurry up, please…",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 67,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 1127769907670464233
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 79,
                    "pathId": -135116970242047054
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8401899341667704895,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "購買部でゼリーなどの食べやすいものを\r\n買いこみ、アグネスタキオンへと届けた。",
            "enText": "We went to the purchasing department and\nbought some jello and other easy to eat\nfoods and delivered them to Agnes Tachyon.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": 4938535827232825998
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": -4051525189479598312
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5255980110895796801,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "ふー……生き返った！",
            "enText": "Whew… is back to life!",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 58,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 127,
                    "pathId": -7533683164846043364
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 128,
                    "pathId": -466612790248141033
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6110153853179551865,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "まったく……\r\n私から目を離すからこうなるんだぞ！",
            "enText": "Totally… This is what happens when\nyou take your eyes off me!",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 47,
                    "pathId": 948618831746493550
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": 1520255027227177781
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6631807076988311439,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "私の助手を名乗るなら、\r\n気をつけてくれたまえよ。",
            "enText": "If you're going to call yourself my\nassistant, you'd better watch your back.",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 77,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": -2763698774283904628
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 88,
                    "pathId": 2033183426836068303
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -606548847037927861,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アグネスタキオン",
            "enName": "Agnes Tachyon",
            "jpText": "そうだ。今後の為にも、君専用の\r\n緊急呼び出しボタンでも開発しておくか。",
            "enText": "That's right. I'll have to develop\na special emergency call button\nfor you for the future.",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 56,
                    "pathId": -279544536490138329
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 2473686671914347156
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5277444444892149951,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "次はないようにしてほしいと頼んだが、\r\nアグネスタキオンは何かを学んだように\n満足そうな顔をしていた。",
            "enText": "I begged him not to do it again, but Agnes\nTachyon looked satisfied, as if she had\nlearned something.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": 308451371544984772
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 40,
                    "pathId": 971770729322450580
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5237163561722358575,
            "blockIdx": 31
        }
    ],
